This is a method of scientific research that researchers are currently pursuing to develop safe and effective treatments for COVID-19.
Other research trends include the development of the COVID-19 vaccine and the transfer of plasma from RNAquine. SARS-CoV-2 contains approximately 66 drug-treatable proteins, each of which contains multiple binding sites.
